"nuestra página. Este método es compatible con la mayoría de bancos españoles "
"y portugueses."
msgstr ""
"The PSD2 online bank transfer payment has no surcharge and is completely "
"secure. You will be redirected to a payment page where you can select your "
"bank and access your online banking to authorise the transfer. Once the "
"payment is complete, you will be automatically redirected back to our page. "
"This method is compatible with most Spanish and Portuguese banks."

